nodes.text: Cr'ann Domp was an individual who lived on the floating city Tolea Biqua, on the planet Genarius. By c. 19 BBY, Domp had became a member of the Tunnel Rats, a criminal gang that operated in the sewers of Tolea Biqua.

In the role-playing adventure The Heart, it is possible for the Tunnel Rats to send Domp to act as a guide for the Heroes of Cularin, to show them the location of a Believer stronghold on Tolea Biqua. The adventure does not identify Domp's species or gender.
